metadata.name: Destiny
metadata.description:
This piece "Destiny" that I created for a derivative art contest of a dear friend (@TDCartofficial), takes me on a new art adventure. I hope this piece can keep you from the chaos of the world for a moment.

No matter how hopeless you feel, take a deep breath, art will help you to find your own destiny.

Procreate
4000x6000px
